summary: The first of four unique bows that will be added to Skyrim.
descriptionHtml: Since most of the weapons mods for Skyrim don\'t include bows,here\'s a little mod that will add 4 unique bows to the game. This is the first of the four bows. The model was made by TonyStalker,and it about 7k pollys now (7048).
author: Kaplan45
